  "text": "Suppose fp k (z) : k = 1; 2; ; K n g are functions having the property that linear combinations can approximate square-integrable functions of z well, in which case g(z i ) 0 n p n (z i ) for some n ; where p n (z) = (p 1 (z); : : : ; p Kn (z)) 0 . De\u2026ning y i;n = y i ; x i;n = x i ; w i;n = p n (z i ); and u i;n = \" i + g(z i ) 0 n w i;n ; the model (4) is of the form (1), and^ n is the series estimator of previously studied by [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] . In this case, our analysis of^ n will proceed under the following assumptions.",
